1
00:00:07,580 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,820
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:30,900
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:39,620
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:39,860 --> 00:00:43,580
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:50,380
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:50,740 --> 00:00:54,340
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:54,620 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:04,940
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:11,700
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:16,700
=Episode 22=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:26,380
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)

18
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:42,000
The grand Gambiered Silk showcase
is about to begin!

19
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,680
The Gambiered Silk showcase is starting?

20
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,680
It's starting?

21
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,800
The grand Gambiered Silk showcase
is beginning?

22
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:47,440
Let's go check it out!

23
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:47,840
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

24
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:48,720
I heard

25
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,280
someone's trying

26
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,440
to restore Gambiered Silk
to its former glory,

27
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,040
so they're holding this showcase.

28
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,080
Come on!

29
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,480
Let's go see
the Gambiered Silk showcase!

30
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:55,760
They say

31
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,440
a lot of big shots
are going to be there!

32
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,400
- Alright!
- Alright!

33
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,400
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

34
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:10,300
(Fine Wine)

35
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,600
Why haven't I heard anything
about my order yet?

36
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,040
You do have stock right here.

37
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,480
Just look at this design

38
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,800
and this texture.

39
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,600
Once you put it on,

40
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:37,080
you're absolutely going to be
the center of attention in Feng City.

41
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,000
Haha.

42
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,800
Indeed.

43
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,800
Remember the pitch
and the attitude I taught you?

44
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,200
I know what to do.

45
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,080
Stop nagging.

46
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:59,000
Folks from right here in Feng City,

47
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,600
friends from all across the land,

48
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,640
welcome to

49
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:06,680
the grand Gambiered Silk showcase!

50
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,800
As we all know,

51
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,480
Feng City's Gambiered Silk carries

52
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:17,600
a heritage spanning a thousand years

53
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,880
and was once designated

54
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:21,640
as a royal tribute,
its fame spreading far and wide.

55
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,080
Although, for various reasons,

56
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,200
its royal tribute status was revoked,

57
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,000
today,

58
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,720
we've come roaring back
with a completely upgraded

59
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,920
Gambiered Silk,

60
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,960
and we're determined

61
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,200
to work toward reclaiming
that royal tribute status.

62
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,040
Yeah!

63
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:42,640
Regarding the making of Gambiered Silk,

64
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,440
some say

65
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:48,080
it takes many processes
of steaming, boiling, and sunning,

66
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:51,600
one tael of gold for every tael of silk.

67
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,400
Others say

68
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,600
it emerges from the mud
yet stays unsoiled,

69
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:58,440
blazing under the scorching sun
in all its splendor.

70
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,040
They're absolutely right.

71
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,400
It's precisely
this painstaking craftsmanship,

72
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,000
combined with the perfect alignment

73
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,720
of the right weather, the right place,
and the right people,

74
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,400
that creates the legend:
nowhere in this world

75
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,920
can you find two pieces
of Gambiered Silk

76
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,360
that are exactly the same.

77
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,600
This is what makes Gambiered Silk

78
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:16,800
the "soft gold" of the textile world.

79
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,520
So today,

80
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:20,160
to ensure the legacy of our ancestors

81
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,000
does not fade into oblivion,

82
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,360
to ensure Gambiered Silk

83
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,120
is not forgotten by the world,

84
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,080
we have spared no expense

85
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:27,560
to hold

86
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,400
this grand Gambiered Silk showcase.

87
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:33,040
It's all to let everyone know

88
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,000
the pride of Feng City,

89
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,120
and to let everyone know

90
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,320
that Feng City's Gambiered Silk

91
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:41,720
still packs a mighty punch.

92
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:50,440
Now, allow me to announce

93
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,920
the Feng City
grand Gambiered Silk showcase

94
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,320
- Officially begins!
- Officially begins!

95
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:59,320
- Great!
- Yeah!

96
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,920
Prince Ning has arrived.

97
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,040
That sure didn't take long.

98
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,680
Li Yunhe, you heartless scumbag!

99
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,840
You leave Yu at home

100
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,000
and drag me out here to get beaten up?

101
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,320
Stay calm.

102
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,200
Everything is going according to plan.

103
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,520
Greetings, Prince Ning.

104
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,800
Long live Your Highness.

105
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,200
What's this?

106
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:50,600
Not exactly a warm welcome
for me in Feng City, is it?

107
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,840
Such insolence!

108
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,440
You dare stand before Prince Ning
and not kneel?

109
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,640
Do you want your entire clan wiped out?

110
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,800
Kneel, quickly!

111
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:57,840
Huh?

112
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,800
I wouldn't dare disrespect you.

113
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,520
I have long admired
your esteemed reputation, Prince Ning.

114
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:02,920
Seeing you so unexpectedly today,

115
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,080
struck by your mighty presence,

116
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,200
I was momentarily dazed.

117
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,840
I beg your generous forgiveness.

118
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,800
Greetings,

119
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,800
Your Highness.

120
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,080
Rise.

121
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,080
I'm traveling incognito

122
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,000
precisely to mingle
with the common folk.

123
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,840
Let's not bother
with all these tedious formalities.

124
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:17,720
Yes,

125
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,280
Your Highness.

126
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,840
My thanks to Your Highness.

127
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,120
Li Yunhe,

128
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,640
His Highness has spoken.

129
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,200
Your grand showcase may now commence.

130
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,000
Alright.

131
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,000
Folks!

132
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,400
Let's have a thunderous round
of applause

133
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:32,400
to welcome Prince Ning

134
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,560
as he graces
the Gambiered Silk revival showcase!

135
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,840
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

136
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,360
Chunxiang,

137
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,160
hurry up and get ready.

138
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:42,400
Alright.

139
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,320
Chunxiang,

140
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:54,120
where have Zhao Yunzhuo and Zhao Ziyao

141
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,120
gone off to?

142
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,400
They were just here a moment ago.

143
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,480
The moment Prince Ning showed up,

144
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,120
they seemed to hurry off in a rush.

145
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,160
I knew it.

146
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,600
Those two siblings can't be relied on.

147
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,080
Hey,

148
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:04,640
wait.

149
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:05,920
Miss Xue,

150
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,240
Prince Ning is right out there.

151
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,640
It's not safe for you
to show your face now.

152
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,120
Chunxiang,

153
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,400
get ready to warm up the crowd.

154
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,600
Isn't that woman

155
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,440
Chunxiang, that maidservant

156
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,280
from the Zhou Manor?

157
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,040
That's right,

158
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:44,840
my lord.

159
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,960
The one on stage right now

160
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:47,960
is indeed Chunxiang,
the head maidservant

161
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,200
of the Zhou Manor.

162
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,560
Well, seems

163
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:56,000
I completely misjudged her.

164
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,800
Never would've guessed that
once this girl changed into this outfit,

165
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,800
she could look so radiant and alluring.

166
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,120
Had I known she had
such hidden potential...

167
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:11,640
Your son has a refreshingly
straightforward personality.

168
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,920
I like that.

169
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,600
Thank you, Your Highness.

170
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,880
Gambiered Silk is truly gorgeous!

171
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:13,120
Mr. Li's designs
are absolutely brilliant.

172
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,920
If we could take this back with us,

173
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:18,640
we'd surely make a massive fortune!

174
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,280
I never expected,
in this small Feng City,

175
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,560
to witness such a uniquely stylish

176
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,920
fashion presentation.

177
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:38,920
Li Yunhe

178
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,520
truly lives up to his reputation.

179
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:46,720
Stop.

180
00:09:57,200 --> 00:10:00,080
May I ask
why Your Highness has called a halt?

181
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,200
A fine horse deserves a fine saddle.

182
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,040
Exquisite garments
are meant for true beauties.

183
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,280
Your Gambiered Silk is fine, yes,

184
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:09,200
but why are they all
just gaudy, powdered faces?

185
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:12,240
Does Feng City truly have
no real beauties?

186
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:15,400
Who says Feng City has no real beauties?

187
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:33,040
Xue Bingxiu,
top courtesan of Chunfeng Pavilion?

188
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,680
What's she doing here?

189
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:35,800
Isn't Xue Bingxiu

190
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,440
supposed to be dead?

191
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,680
Guards!

192
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:47,200
This woman is a traitor and a rebel!

193
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,320
Seize her at once!

194
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,640
Uncle,

195
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:59,120
it's been a while.

196
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,960
Zhao Ziyao?

197
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,320
Ziyao,

198
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,240
what brings you to Feng City as well?

199
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,680
What did you just call him?

200
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,440
He's my uncle.

201
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:15,280
My father was the late emperor.

202
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,520
Prince Ning is my second uncle.

203
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,080
So,

204
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,800
Li Yunhe,

205
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,280
now that you've witnessed
my divine countenance,

206
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,880
do you still not kneel
and pay your respects?

207
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,960
So you're a princess?

208
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,240
Then your brother

209
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,400
Zhao Yunzhuo...

210
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,880
Protect the princess!

211
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,560
Hurry!

212
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,200
Move!

213
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,000
For a matter as monumental
as restoring Gambiered Silk

214
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,040
to the royal tribute list,

215
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:57,200
how could I possibly not be present?

216
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,920
My dear uncle,

217
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,840
what "traitor and rebel"
are you trying to arrest here?

218
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,040
What?

219
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,240
Zhao Ziyao is a princess?

220
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,120
Zhao Yunzhuo is the emperor?

221
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,680
What a spectacle!

222
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,840
What a marvelous performance
you've staged.

223
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:21,120
However, the reigning emperor
is still in the capital.

224
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,040
Who are you

225
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,200
to dare impersonate His Majesty?

226
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:26,400
Guards!

227
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,960
Arrest them all!

228
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,120
Protect His Majesty!

229
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,200
Let's go!

230
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,240
Another rebellion?

231
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,600
Good thing

232
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,480
I came prepared.

233
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,200
We defend the emperor of Daqian!

234
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:24,240
Marquis of Zhennan,

235
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,200
with things as they stand,

236
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,720
do you truly mean to stick to rebellion
to its bitter end?

237
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:29,760
Marquis of Zhennan,

238
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,600
even if you surrender right now,

239
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,880
do you think he would ever let you live?

240
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,000
If you don't finish him off
here and now,

241
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,440
watch as your entire clan is wiped out.

242
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:43,440
Sworn warriors of the Marquis House!

243
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,200
Seal the entire city!

244
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,600
Not a single soul is to leave!

245
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,240
Not even the rats

246
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:54,920
shall leave Feng City alive!

247
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,440
Marquis of Zhennan, you have some nerve!

248
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,480
I am the emperor of Daqian!

249
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,240
Throw down your weapons, all of you!

250
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,040
Surrender at once!

251
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:05,520
Haha!

252
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:09,000
You claim to be the emperor, so you are?

253
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:11,080
Then I can be the emperor too!

254
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:14,600
Such insolence in my own territory?

255
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,400
Today, every last one of you will die.

256
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,720
Especially you, Li Yunhe!

257
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:25,400
Leave no one standing. Charge!

258
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,080
Your Majesty,

259
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:32,960
we must retreat, quickly!

260
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,520
Our soldiers can't hold out much longer!

261
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:35,680
Prince Ning,

262
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:37,600
do you truly believe

263
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,960
you can emerge as the final victor?

264
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,120
What empty bluster.

265
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:43,120
All of Feng City is under my control,

266
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,200
and the Marquis of Zhennan
stands at my side.

267
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,680
What do you have to win with?

268
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:49,120
For all your cunning calculations,

269
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,800
you still fell one move short.

270
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,680
Mere theatrics.

271
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:54,680
My friend,

272
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:57,200
from here on, everything rests on you.

273
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,120
So the one you're counting on

274
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,440
is that fool

275
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,120
Li Yunhe?

276
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:04,880
He's a mere nobody
kicked out by the Zhous.

277
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,480
What makes him qualified

278
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,880
to even enter this power game?

279
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,480
What qualifies me?

280
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,880
The fact that a greedy fool
like you just couldn't stop.

281
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:15,760
Marquis of Zhennan,

282
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:18,320
perhaps
you still haven't figured it out yet.

283
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,720
That precious son of yours

284
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,400
used nearly the entire fortune

285
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:23,080
of your household

286
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:25,080
to hoard grain at inflated prices.

287
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,160
I'm afraid your household

288
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,680
can't even produce

289
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:29,080
a single coin anymore.

290
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:29,800
You...

291
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:30,360
That's not true,

292
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,080
Father.

293
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:31,800
Father.

294
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,680
Thanks to you,

295
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,320
Yunzhuo and I

296
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:37,080
actually made a tidy fortune.

297
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:37,960
What?

298
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,040
You foolish wretch!

299
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:39,680
Father!

300
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:40,320
Stay calm!

301
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:42,760
So what if they made a pile?
They'll die right away!

302
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:43,520
All soldiers, hear my command!

303
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:44,600
Charge!

304
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,880
You wouldn't dare.

305
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,360
Lu Qifeng,

306
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:48,400
take a guess.

307
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:51,120
When you're broke,
and I'm flush with cash,

308
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,600
what do you think is going to happen?

309
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,080
At your command,

310
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,400
Mr. Li.

311
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:04,480
I'm here to report for duty

312
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,600
with the guys.

313
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,440
You...

314
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,120
Unbelievable, Long Er.

315
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:11,800
You dare betray the Marquis House?

316
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,280
We worked

317
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:16,680
to our bones for the Marquis House,

318
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,920
and every month we barely
scraped together a little silver,

319
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:21,760
which you then snatched back
to blow on your grain hoarding!

320
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:24,280
Yunhe is a man of unshakable honor.

321
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:26,360
If I didn't lead the guys
to abandon the darkness for the light,

322
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,320
what was I supposed to do?

323
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,400
Follow a conscienceless scumbag like you

324
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,760
and starve?

325
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,160
Guys! For Feng City,

326
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,280
charge!

327
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:10,780
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

328
00:17:10,940 --> 00:17:14,140
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

329
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:17,380
♪Who took the March rain♪

330
00:17:17,620 --> 00:17:20,980
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

331
00:17:21,340 --> 00:17:24,140
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

332
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:27,500
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

333
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:34,300
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

334
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:37,780
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

335
00:17:38,020 --> 00:17:40,860
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

336
00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:43,300
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

337
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:47,500
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

338
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:50,860
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

339
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:54,140
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

340
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:57,580
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

341
00:17:57,740 --> 00:18:04,260
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

342
00:18:30,540 --> 00:18:34,060
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

343
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:37,460
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

344
00:18:38,060 --> 00:18:40,780
♪Who took the March rain♪

345
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:44,300
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

346
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:47,580
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

347
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:51,380
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

348
00:18:51,420 --> 00:18:54,700
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

349
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:57,660
♪As seasons change♪

350
00:18:57,660 --> 00:19:01,300
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

351
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:04,140
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

352
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:06,780
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

353
00:19:06,780 --> 00:19:10,860
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

354
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:14,180
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

355
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:17,900
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

356
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:21,420
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

357
00:19:21,420 --> 00:19:24,300
♪Only for you♪

358
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:27,900
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

359
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:30,780
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

360
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:33,460
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

361
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:37,540
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

362
00:19:37,540 --> 00:19:40,860
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

363
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:44,260
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

364
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:50,780
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

365
00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:55,980
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

366
00:19:57,260 --> 00:20:01,780
♪Your wedding gown♪
